text:
Here's the birthday prezzie I
couldn't give you! And I have to
say it again: HAPPY BIRTHDAY!!!!!
I sent this as fast as I could! I hope
you love, adore, and maybe even
cherish it!

Here's the birthday prezzie I was
going to give you, but your pockets
were full. I really wanted to get
something, you know, special?
So I SUUUUPER hope you love it!

That birthday prezzie I wasn't able
to give you? Here it is!

celebrate. I attached the birthday

HAAAPPY BIRTHDAAAY!!
